..................uploading........................
...................................................

well hopefully youve extracted this right
you should have the following files

------- news (folder)
--------------- images (sub dir)
----------- readme
----------- news.php
----------- conf.php // edit this one
----------- install.php
----------- header.php
----------- footer.php
----------- connect.php
----------- admin.php
----------- login.php
----------- style.css

so when you upload you show called a folder 
called "news" with everything in there




...................................................
..............editing conf.php.....................
...................................................


just fill in your database details





...................................................
.................once edited.......................
...................................................

surf to http://yourdomain/news/install.php
once installed and youve seen all green ticks 
(note if you see red ticks something is wrong with your details)
go to login.php






...................................................
..........Get the news on my index page............
...................................................

use the following code on your homepage assuming its index.php..

include("./news/news.php");




and thats it really :)



